@startuml
title Ocean View Resort - UML Component Diagram

' A4 landscape-oriented layout tuning
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
left to right direction
scale max 1600 width
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam ranksep 70
skinparam nodesep 35
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "Admin / Staff / Guest" as User

node "Client Layer" {
  component "JSP Views\n(common, admin, staff, guest)" as JSP
  component "Client Scripts\n(validation.js, charts.js)" as ClientJS
  component "Chart.js Runtime" as ChartJS
}

node "Application Layer (Tomcat)" {
  component "Security Filters\n(AuthFilter, RoleFilter)" as Filters
  component "Web Controllers\n(Servlets by module)" as Controllers
  component "Reporting API\n(ReportApiServlet)" as ReportAPI
  component "Business Services\n(RegisterService,\nReservationService,\nBillingService)" as Services
  component "DAO Components\n(JDBC DAO Implementations)" as DAOs
  component "Utility Components\n(DBConnection,\nPasswordUtil,\nAuthRedirectUtil)" as Utils
}

database "MySQL Database\n(oceanview_resort)" as MySQL

User --> JSP : Browser interaction
JSP --> Filters : HTTP request
Filters --> Controllers : allowed request
Controllers --> Services : business operation
Controllers --> DAOs : direct data operation
ReportAPI --> DAOs : report data queries
ClientJS --> ReportAPI : /api/reports/*
ClientJS --> ChartJS : render charts
Services --> DAOs : persistence access
DAOs --> Utils : open JDBC connection
Utils --> MySQL : connection setup
DAOs --> MySQL : SQL CRUD / queries
Controllers --> JSP : forward/redirect response

@enduml
